00:01:10,730 --> 00:01:12,470
What do you mean?

5
00:01:12,470 --> 00:01:13,900
You made a vow.

6
00:01:13,900 --> 00:01:15,640
Just go back to being an angel.

7
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:18,600
This is my real vow.

8
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:22,080
I'm sorry.

9
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:24,710
Even if I become unhappy,

10
00:01:24,710 --> 00:01:27,590
or can't become an angel again,

11
00:01:28,370 --> 00:01:30,580
I want to stay by Woohyun.

12
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:34,000
Even if it means disappearing forever after living as a human?

13
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:38,980
Even if I disappear forever.

14
00:01:40,510 --> 00:01:44,730
You... will... regret it.

15
00:01:49,630 --> 00:01:52,560
Thank you for everything, Senior.

16
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:55,040
I won't forget it.

17
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,950
I'm...

18
00:01:57,950 --> 00:01:59,880
going to forget you.

