00:40:57,910 --> 00:41:00,870
Even so,

529
00:41:02,150 --> 00:41:09,280
if you know his name, social security number, or even the last place he lived, I could help you look for him.

530
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:15,460
To others, parents are like a fence. But to me, they're like a cliff.

531
00:41:15,460 --> 00:41:19,990
A cliff so high...

532
00:41:19,990 --> 00:41:23,780
that you can't see.

533
00:41:23,780 --> 00:41:27,720
If you fall, you'll die.

534
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:30,050
So, please don't look for him.

535
00:41:30,050 --> 00:41:33,040
That will help me the most.

536
00:41:35,520 --> 00:41:38,570
If those men come again,

537
00:41:38,570 --> 00:41:40,370
contact me immediately.

538
00:41:40,370 --> 00:41:41,990
All right?

539
00:41:46,100 --> 00:41:49,090
The adults probably had their own reasons.

540
00:41:49,090 --> 00:41:51,690
Let's cheer up.

541
00:41:57,100 --> 00:41:59,450
What really happened to you?

542
00:41:59,450 --> 00:42:00,770
That's really a talent.

543
00:42:00,770 --> 00:42:02,830
How can you get fired six times in one day?

544
00:42:02,830 --> 00:42:05,160
Are 24 hours not enough?

545
00:42:05,160 --> 00:42:07,980
You're right. Isn't there anything else I can do?

546
00:42:07,980 --> 00:42:09,210
That's it.

547
00:42:09,210 --> 00:42:12,760
I'm surprised that you study well with that kind of brain.

548
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:14,560
You probably don't have time to study

549
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:15,960
if you're always working hard like this.

550
00:42:15,960 --> 00:42:16,930
Bingo!

551
00:42:16,930 --> 00:42:22,520
It's because I don't have time. If I did, you guys wouldn't be able to keep up with me.

552
00:42:22,520 --> 00:42:23,540
Let's figure something out.

553
00:42:23,540 --> 00:42:25,020
Sure.

554
00:42:33,040 --> 00:42:34,230
Seulbi!

555
00:42:34,230 --> 00:42:35,330
Sungyeol!

556
00:42:35,330 --> 00:42:36,930
Where were you all this time?

557
00:42:36,930 --> 00:42:38,940
Kisook introduced me to some part-time jobs.

558
00:42:38,940 --> 00:42:42,160
I wanted to raise some money, even if it was a little bit.

559
00:42:42,160 --> 00:42:44,280
Are you hurt somewhere?

560
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:45,380
No.

561
00:42:45,380 --> 00:42:47,150
Aren't you pushing yourself too hard?

562
00:42:47,150 --> 00:42:50,850
It's okay. I'm really strong.

563
00:42:50,850 --> 00:42:52,130
But what brings you here?

564
00:42:52,130 --> 00:42:54,390
I stopped by because I was curious.

565
00:42:54,390 --> 00:42:56,510
I'll try to find a way to raise money.

566
00:42:56,510 --> 00:43:00,290
So don't overdo yourself and don't worry.

567
00:43:00,290 --> 00:43:05,440
Thank you. Woohyun would be very thankful.

568
00:43:05,440 --> 00:43:08,350
All right, go inside and rest.

569
00:43:14,950 --> 00:43:18,810
What were you doing all this time?

570
00:43:18,810 --> 00:43:21,600
Did you wait for me?

571
00:43:21,600 --> 00:43:23,730
Don't do useless things.

572
00:43:23,730 --> 00:43:25,810
There's nothing you can do.

573
00:43:25,810 --> 00:43:29,090
If I look, I'm sure there's something.

574
00:43:29,090 --> 00:43:30,910
You want to find my father?

575
00:43:30,910 --> 00:43:32,390
You can't do it, right?

576
00:43:32,390 --> 00:43:34,170
You want to pay all the debt?!

577
00:43:34,170 --> 00:43:35,440
You can't do it, right?!

578
00:43:35,440 --> 00:43:38,430
So, please don't do anything!

579
00:43:38,430 --> 00:43:41,180
I really can't understand (you).

580
00:43:41,180 --> 00:43:43,880
Why is it so hard?

581
00:43:43,880 --> 00:43:50,240
Why is it so hard to get you to laugh and to eat?

582
00:43:50,240 --> 00:43:54,950
I don't know how hurt you are or how sad you are.

583
00:43:54,950 --> 00:43:57,350
If you don't know then stay still!

584
00:43:57,350 --> 00:44:00,780
You can't just stay like this. I know this much.

585
00:44:13,130 --> 00:44:16,220
 That's why I said to leave, you idiot.

