 You two look good together

676
00:53:11,490 --> 00:53:12,350
 Hey!

677
00:53:12,350 --> 00:53:13,190
 You're really best friends, right?

678
00:53:13,190 --> 00:53:14,380
 - Oh, hey! 
 - Oh, hey!

